average-position-help: The average position for all keywords on the last day in the selected period.
confirm-cancel: You've made changes, are you sure you want to cancel?
cpc-help: CPC (Cost Per Click) is the suggested bid for advertising in Google AdWords. The value is calculated by taking into account the cost per click that advertisers are paying for this keyword in the chosen search engine and location. The amount is only an estimation and the actual CPC may vary.
http-tooltip: This page is not secured with HTTPS which may negatively impact your ranking.
https-tooltip: This page is secured with HTTPS.
name: Name
pos-change-help: The net sum of all gained and lost positions across all of the website‘s keywords during the selected period.
position-distribution-help: Keyword position distribution for the latest position in the selected period.
traffic-help: Traffic is the estimated number of clicks each month and is calculated from the keywords' search volume multiplied by the (roughly) estimated CTR for the current position.
volume-help: Search volume is the estimated number of searches made for the keyword each month in the search engine that is connected to your website.

plan-features.admin-role-info: Invite users that can view and manage data but are prohibited from managing your plan and billing information.
plan-features.api-info: Access your data via our REST API to build custom tools and integrations.
plan-features.chart-exports-info: Export any chart‘s data to a CSV or Excel file.
plan-features.external-role-info: Invite external read-only users that are restricted to viewing data in selected projects.
plan-features.locations-info: Track your rankings in specific locations. This could be for instance a country, region or city.
plan-features.manual-ranking-refresh-info: Refresh your keywords' rankings on demand if you can‘t wait until the next day for fresh data.
plan-features.member-role-info: Invite users that can view and manage website data in selected projects.
plan-features.multiple-users-info: Invite more users to your account.
plan-features.project-permissions-info: Give your team members and external users access to specific projects only.
plan-features.white-labeling-info: Upload your own logo and remove all traces of Wincher and our branding in the reports sent to your team and customers.
plan-features.multiple-reports-info: Schedule as many reports as you want to yourself, your team or your customers.
